    • コンストラクタの詳細

      • Dvector

        public Dvector(BasicID[] basicIDs)
        Use all waveforms in the IDs Weighting factor is reciprocal of maximum value in each obs time window
        パラメータ:
        basicIDs - must contain waveform data

      • Dvector

        public Dvector(BasicID[] basicIDs,
               java.util.function.Predicate<BasicID> chooser)
        chooserを通った波形のみを使う 観測波形を選別しその観測波形に対する理論波形を用いる Weighting factor is reciprocal of maximum value in each obs time window
        パラメータ:
        basicIDs - must contain waveform data
        chooser - Predicate

      • Dvector

        public Dvector(BasicID[] basicIDs,
               java.util.function.Predicate<BasicID> chooser,
               java.util.function.ToDoubleBiFunction<BasicID,BasicID> weightingFunction)
        chooserを通った観測波形のみを使う 観測波形を選別しその観測波形に対する理論波形を用いる
        パラメータ:
        basicIDs - must contain waveform data
        chooser - Predicate used for filtering Observed (not synthetic) ID if one ID is true, then the observed ID and the pair synethetic are used.
        weightingFunction - ToDoubleBiFunction (observed, synthetic)
